        "id": "mineru_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_0",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "Gender",
        "bbox": [
          0.39666666666666667,
          0.088,
          0.6046666666666667,
          0.16266666666666665
        ],
        "order": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_1",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "It has long been acknowledged that there may be differences in language usage between men and women: quite extreme in languages other than English",
        "bbox": [
          0.058666666666666666,
          0.23822222222222222,
          0.8953333333333333,
          0.4488888888888889
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "• Lakoff (1975) identified extensive differences not just in grammar and lexis, but in aspects of style, register, and (especially in dialogues) dynamic roles",
        "bbox": [
          0.05466666666666667,
          0.4577777777777778,
          0.9173333333333333,
          0.6168888888888889
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Studies have adapted to the broader social agenda: early theories relating to power relationships between sexes (Lakoff) now giving way to view that there is a cultural difference (Tannen)",
        "bbox": [
          0.06333333333333334,
          0.6266666666666667,
          0.9293333333333333,
          0.8373333333333334
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_PPT_sociolinguistics_page_015_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "• We'll look at this issue in more detail later",
        "bbox": [
          0.06,
          0.8471111111111111,
          0.766,
          0.8977777777777778
        ],
        "order": 5
      }
    ]
  }
